title: Ep - 139 - JENNIFER WELCH FROM SWEET HOME
description:
Jennifer Welch is an established commercial and residential interior designer and the star of Sweet Home on Bravo. She talks about how the show has evolved, how she roped some of her clients into appearing on Sweet Home, and gives great tips for sprucing up your place so it looks like you live in a swanky hotel. 


Rob Cesternino is a former Survivor contestant turned podcast host. He discusses the current season of Survivor and provides most interesting answers to a multitude of questions about what it is like to be on the show and what life is like after you return. 


Betches writer Shannon McCormick reports about her evening at SUR and how the events that enfolded that evening made its way to the premiere of Vanderpump Rules.
